  "heading_path": "中文学术纯文风 Humanize Skill：生产化交付与红队报告 / 22. 第十八轮：detector-only 运行时、来源负例权限与 runner 诊断 / 22.2 红队发现 negative guard 绕过了来源信任矩阵",
  "intensity": "STRUCTURAL",
  "line_count": 29,
  "masked_text": "[[PROTECTED:F00001-P01416:4d4eb1d4bec3]]\n后验审计逐张反查当前 10 张负例卡的来源类别。v17 policy 只允许 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P01417:d6276834a9f4]] 与\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P01418:cfb0fbc3d5b7]] 使用 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P01419:df6f9ffc9e3c]]，代码却把以下 6 张无此权限的卡全部标为\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P01420:144d42912eb1]] 并送入投影：\n\n- [[PROTECTED:F00001-P01421:ab55dba8ddc3]]：[[PROTECTED:F00001-P01422:747f7bc4138c]]；\n- [[PROTECTED:F00001-P01423:8a73eae34e62]]：[[PROTECTED:F00001-P01424:747f7bc4138c]]；\n- [[PROTECTED:F00001-P01425:d5b4824ae3ce]]：[[PROTECTED:F00001-P01426:747f7bc4138c]]；\n- [[PROTECTED:F00001-P01427:67d9509fd692]]：[[PROTECTED:F00001-P01428:70820b1169c0]]；\n- [[PROTECTED:F00001-P01429:fd2df6e4f5a7]]：[[PROTECTED:F00001-P01430:384aeb6b0f97]]；\n- [[PROTECTED:F00001-P01431:c0789f47ce37]]：[[PROTECTED:F00001-P01432:747f7bc4138c]]。\n\n这不是命名瑕疵。[[PROTECTED:F00001-P01433:7db6375d5ae0]] 在固定 policy 中只允许 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P01434:43abf5471430]]；[[PROTECTED:F00001-P01435:747f7bc4138c]] 只允许\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P01436:b6a27ad29422]]。让这些卡进入 production finalizer，相当于把[[PROTECTED:F00001-P01437:d15affe9c36d]]\n扩大成[[PROTECTED:F00001-P01438:dae9ac51285e]]。v17 的 ROLE fresh fixture 又只测试 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P01439:7cc6a66c4586]]，测不到这条旁路。\n\nv18 在三个位置同时修复：\n\n1. 完整 builder 按固定 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P01440:902b54d29eeb]] 计算 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P01441:bda8fa0faa56]]；无权限卡变为\n   [[PROTECTED:F00001-P01442:f9c55795f75f]]，不会伪装成普通 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P01443:940542ecc5db]]。\n2. candidate queue 自动扫描跳过 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P01444:f9c55795f75f]]；只有明确获权且 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P01445:144d42912eb1]] 的卡执行。\n3. projection transform 使用同一冻结 trust policy 过滤；本地给 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P01446:0646bcc1f77f]] 追加\n   [[PROTECTED:F00001-P01447:df6f9ffc9e3c]] 会因整张决策矩阵漂移而构建失败。\n\n修复后的完整安装版为 17 张 provisional positive、4 张 runtime negative guard、6 张 audit-only\nnegative definition；production positive 仍为 0。四张 runtime guard 分别覆盖\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P01448:6359c3ecae84]]，来源均为明确模型文本或模型来源未解析文本。\n\n",
